thread.title: Candice Forward

author: Candice Forward
title: Candice Forward
text: WOW!!! We are so happy with the website Havealook created for our new company. It turned out better than we envisioned! The whole process was so much easier than I thought it was going to be. The online tutorials that explain how you manage your website after it is designed is very easy to understand. The support guys have been so patient with me and what little changes I wanted done. Couldn't be more happier!!!
